data.description: Just reduced!!!! This beautiful townhome situated in the highly sought-after Valencia neighborhood. Built in 2018, this residence offers a 1,760 square feet making it one of the largest townhomes.  This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features only one common wall, ensuring a sense of privacy. The main level has a bright living space, with natural light from the large windows, creating a welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen, designed with quartz countertops, Stainless steel appliances and upgraded kitchen cabinets provide storage for all your cooking needs. Upstairs is the master bedroom along with two additional bedrooms. The master suite features a spacious layout and an ensuite bathroom. This townhome has a spacious loft on the upper level, can be use as a office/study area or a play space for children. For environmentally conscious homeowners, this property is equipped with a Tesla charger in the garage, catering to Tesla owners. The Valencia neighborhood offers a wealth of amenities. Enjoy parks, playgrounds, and walking trails, perfect for outdoor activities and leisurely strolls. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhome your own. Schedule a showing today.
